---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '~/components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Retail — KKT"
  description="AI and PMO delivery for mid-sized retailers. The full playbook lives at retail.kittykat.tech."
  ogImage="/og/retail.png"
>
  <article class="prose-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Industries — Retail</div>
      <h1 class="h1-page">For mid-sized retailers.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Margin, cash, customer ownership, decision speed. We work where AI
        and PMO discipline earn their place against measurable outcomes — not
        where they look good in a slide.
      </p>

      <section class="callout">
        <div class="callout-label">The retail playbook</div>
        <h2 class="callout-title">Retail AI Canvas — 30 services across 11 domains.</h2>
        <p class="callout-body">
          A full open playbook of where AI and PMO discipline create measurable
          value across a mid-sized retailer. Built from real engagements,
          updated quarterly, with an advisor that walks you through it.
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://retail.kittykat.tech" class="btn-primary" rel="noopener">
            Open the playbook →
          </a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="starts">
        <div class="section-label">Engagement starting points</div>
        <h2 class="h2-section">Where retail engagements typically begin.</h2>
        <p class="starts-lede">
          Diagnostics surface different priorities for different
          retailers. These four show up the most often as the first
          workstream worth shipping.
        </p>

        <div class="starts-grid">
          <div class="start-card">
            <h3 class="start-title">Margin recovery and assortment.</h3>
            <p>
              Where margin is being left on the shelf, and what to do
              about it. Data-grounded, decision-shaped, often the
              fastest line to measurable money in.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="start-card">
            <h3 class="start-title">Customer ownership.</h3>
            <p>
              Segmentation, lifecycle, and the operating decisions that
              follow from knowing who actually drives the business.
              Compounds over time.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="start-card">
            <h3 class="start-title">Decision cadence.</h3>
            <p>
              Pricing, replenishment, cash discipline as a daily
              rhythm rather than a quarterly review. PMO discipline is
              what makes that rhythm hold.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="start-card">
            <h3 class="start-title">Foundational data and reporting.</h3>
            <p>
              When the core is shaky, everything downstream stays
              shaky. If the diagnostic surfaces this, we start there
              before reaching for AI.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="starts-tail">
          The full playbook lives at
          <a href="https://retail.kittykat.tech" rel="noopener">retail.kittykat.tech</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <CTA
      heading="Retail diagnostic, two weeks."
      body="A focused look at where the playbook applies to your business — what to ship first, what to leave alone, what proof you need to commit."
    />
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-page {
    padding-top: clamp(40px, 6vh, 72px);
  }
  .section-label { margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .h1-page {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.16;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .callout {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .callout-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .callout-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px);
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .callout-body {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .starts {
    margin-top: 56px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .starts .section-label { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .starts h2 { margin-bottom: 18px; max-width: 24ch; }
  .starts-lede {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .starts-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .starts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  .start-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
  }
  .start-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .start-card p { font-size: 15px; max-width: 50ch; }
  .starts-tail {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  .starts-tail a {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .starts-tail a:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; text-decoration-color: var(--accent); }
</style>
